* Foreword

 Here are resources of pin location of the chips which are used to make Ese-SCC cartridges and perform your own modifications.

 I chose 1 M ROM of the type relatively frequently used for mega ROM games as my example.ÅB

 By looking at this, you will learn that ROMs and RAMs have similar pin location, won't you?
 Taking advantage of this makes the work easy.

 Use this resource together with wiring diagram and actual SCC games for achievement of better understanding.

 For execution of these Ics, it's better to refer to the data disclosed from each product makers.


